  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    ResultsCommunicationPane
    A ResultsCommunicationPane is a class that represents a multipane containing the bar and pie chart of the performed communication obtained from the performed simulation.
    ResultsComputingPowerPane
    A ResultsComputingPowerPane is a class that represents a multipane containing the bar charts showing the information about the computing power use for machines, users and tasks.
    ResultsDialog
    A ResultsDialog class is used to display a window containing all types of information from the performed simulation.
    ResultsGlobalPane
    A ResultsGlobalPane is a class used to display the general results from the performed simulation.
    ResultsProcessingPane
    A ResultsProcessingPane is a class that represents a multipane containing the bar and pie chart of the performed processing obtained from the performed simulation.
    ResultsResourcePane
    A ResultsResourcePane is a class that represents a pane containing the information about all the processing and communication performed of each simulated component.
    ResultsTasksPane
    A ResultsTasksPane is a class that represents a pane containing the information about processing and communication performed for resolve the tasks.
    ResultsUsersPane
    A ResultsUsersPane is a class that represents a pane containing the information about processing and communication performed for resolve the tasks for each user.
    SimulationResultChartMaker
    A SimulationResultChartMaker class is used to create charts of multiples types containing information from simulation results.
